These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-1::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, hedgehog, goat, horse
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, chef, firefighter, police-officer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, d&b, rock, techno
 1. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
 2. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
 3. the fan rock is not to the right of the fan d&b##8
 4. the fan d&b is not to the left of the police-officer##8
 5. the owner of the bird is in an even position##4
 6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the fan rock##1
 7. the analyst is the fan country##1
 8. the fan rock is not the police-officer##6
 9. the fan d&b is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goat##5
10. the owner of the goat is not to the right of the firefighter##8
11. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the left of the owner of the goat##8
12. the fan d&b is between the owner of the goat and the chef##2
13. the fan rock and the firefighter have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |     3     |    4    |
| Hobby         | goat | hedgehog      | horse | bird |
| Job           | firefighter | police-officer | chef      | analyst |
| Music-Genre   | rock        | d&b            | techno    | country |

