There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, dutch, egyptian, italian
4 different pets are kept: bird, guinea-pig, mouse, turtle
 1. the fan techno is not to the left of the chinese##8
 2. the egyptian is on the left of the fan blues##1
 3. the egyptian is the fan techno##1
 4. the egyptian is somewhere between the italian and the owner of the guinea-pig##7
 5. the fan house and the chinese have different parity positions##9
 6. the owner of the mouse is not to the right of the fan techno##8
 7. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the italian##5
 8. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the right of the fan house##5
 9. the dutch is on the left of the chinese##1
10. the owner of the bird is between the chinese and the owner of the turtle##2
11. the fan blues is not the chinese##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |    4    |
| Hobby         | house | punk     | techno  | blues |
| Nationality   | dutch       | chinese    | egyptian | italian |
| Pet           | mouse       | guinea-pig | bird     | turtle  |

