 2. the person eating apricot and the person who likes ebony have different parity positions##9
 3. the person driving the van is the person who likes emerald##1
 4. the person who likes white is not to the right of the person driving the skateboard##8
 5. the person who likes emerald is somewhere to the left of the person who likes white##5
 6. the person who likes white and the person eating cabbage have different parity positions##9
 7. the person who likes ebony is somewhere to the left of the person eating blueberry##5
 8. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
 9. the person eating apricot and the person who likes pink have the same parity positions##9
10. the person driving the van is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person eating radish is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage    | emerald | white | ebony      | pink        |
| Food        | cabbage  | apricot       | radish     | blueberry  |
